alue":"Someone turned the request down. It stops there and won't move forward. A reason is required."},{"label":"Escalated","value":"The request was bumped up, usually on its own after a step waited too long."},{"label":"Cancelled","value":"The request was cancelled. It stops there."},{"label":"AutoApproved","value":"The amount was small enough to be approved on its own, so no one had to act on that step."}]},{"heading":"Decision Types (History)","items":[{"label":"Approve","value":"The approver accepts, and the request moves to the next step or finishes."},{"label":"Reject","value":"The approver turns it down. A reason is required and the request stops there."},{"label":"Delegate","value":"The approver hands the decision to someone else. The request stays on the same step under the new person."},{"label":"Escalate","value":"The request is bumped up, usually on its own when a step waits past its reminder window."}]},{"heading":"Workflows Tab (Manager / Admin only)","items":[{"label":"New Workflow button","value":"Starts a new approval. The green button at the top of the Workflows tab."},{"label":"Workflows list","value":"Shows every approval you've set up, with its name, what it approves, whether it's on or off, how many steps it has, and when it was made. Click a row to open it."},{"label":"Active / Inactive label","value":"A green 'Active' label when the approval is turned on, or a grey 'Inactive' label when it's off."},{"label":"Edit (pencil button)","value":"Opens the approval so you can change its settings and steps."}]},{"heading":"Workflow Setup — Top Fields","items":[{"label":"Workflow Name (required)","value":"The name people will see, such as 'PO Approval over $500'. Needed before you can save."},{"label":"Entity Type (required)","value":"What this approval covers: a purchase order, expense, quote, time entry, or sales order. Needed before you can save."},{"label":"Description","value":"An optional note explaining what this approval is for."},{"label":"Amount Threshold","value":"Optional. The approval only kicks in when the amount is above this number."}]},{"heading":"Workflow Setup — Step Fields (Repeatable)","items":[{"label":"Step Number","value":"Numbered 1, 2, 3 in the order the steps appear. Steps happen one after another."},{"label":"Step Name (required)","value":"A label for the step, such as 'Manager Approval'."},{"label":"Approver Type","value":"Who signs off on this step: a specific person, a role, or the requester's own manager."},{"label":"Role","value":"Shown only when the approver is a role. Choose Manager, Admin, Office Manager, or Project Manager."},{"label":"Auto-Approve Below","value":"Optional. If the amount is under this number, the step approves on its own."},{"label":"Escalate After (Hours)","value":"Optional. If the step waits longer than this many hours, it's bumped up on its own."},{"label":"Add Step / Remove Step","value":"Add Step adds another sign-off. The trash button removes a step (shown only when there's more than one)."}]},{"heading":"Rules","items":[{"label":"Workflow Name","value":"Needed before you can save the approval."},{"label":"Entity Type","value":"Needed before you can save the approval."},{"label":"Step Name","value":"Needed on every step."},{"label":"At least one step","value":"The Save button stays greyed out until the approval has at least one step and everything's filled in."},{"label":"Reject reason","value":"Needed before you can confirm turning a request down."}]},{"heading":"What Can Be Approved","items":[{"label":"Purchase Order","value":"Sign-off on a purchase order — the most common use."},{"label":"Expense","value":"Sign-off on an expense or reimbursement."},{"label":"Quote","value":"Sign-off on a sales quote before it goes to the customer."},{"label":"Time Entry","value":"Sign-off on a time entry, such as overtime. It has no dollar amount, so the Amount column shows a dash."},{"label":"Sales Order","value":"Sign-off on a sales order, such as a large order or special terms."}]}]}"""
